  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Software Engineer",
  "description": "<p>We are looking for a <strong>Software Engineer</strong> with a strong interest in software development to join our development team. This role is suitable for <strong>fresh graduates or candidates with up to 1–2 years of working experience</strong> who are eager to learn and grow in a professional software development environment.</p><h3>Responsibilities</h3><ol><li><p>Design, develop, test, and maintain software applications using <strong>C# (.NET)</strong></p></li><li><p>Develop and maintain <strong>MS SQL Server</strong> databases, including queries, stored procedures, and basic performance tuning</p></li><li><p>Assist in software requirement analysis and technical design</p></li><li><p>Perform debugging, testing, and issue resolution</p></li><li><p>Participate in code reviews and follow coding standards and best practices</p></li><li><p>Work closely with team members to deliver software solutions on schedule<br /></p><h3>Requirements</h3><ol><li><p><strong>Diploma or higher qualification</strong> in Computer Science, Software Engineering, Information Technology, or related field</p></li><li><p>Fresh graduate or <strong>1–2 years of relevant working experience</strong></p></li><li><p>Basic knowledge of <strong>C# / .NET development</strong></p></li><li><p>Strong interest and passion for <strong>software development and problem-solving</strong></p></li><li>Willingness to learn new technologies and improve technical skills</li><li><p>Good analytical thinking and attention to detail</p></li></ol></li></ol>",
